(7, 'Celestron C9,25,   William optics Megrez Triplet Fluorite refractor 80/480mm', '', '', 'Brand/Type of Camera: CCD Starlight Xpress SXVF M8C<br>Framesize: 2312 x 1720 <br>Color / BW Chip: Color<br>CCD Chip Type: Sony ICX406AQ SuperHAD CCD <br><br>Description of Back-End Equipment:<br>Losmandy GM8 mount, ', 7),
